hu.akarnokd.rxjava2.subjects

Class DispatchWorkSubject<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.reactivex.Observable<T>
      • io.reactivex.subjects.Subject<T>
        • hu.akarnokd.rxjava2.subjects.DispatchWorkSubject<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the input and output value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    io.reactivex.disposables.Disposable, io.reactivex.ObservableSource<T>, io.reactivex.Observer<T>

    public final class DispatchWorkSubject<T>
extends io.reactivex.subjects.Subject<T>
implements io.reactivex.disposables.Disposable
    A Subject variant that queues up items and dispatches them asynchronously so that one of the currently subscribed Observers can pick it up one by one, otherwise* cache it until at least an Observer subscribes.
    Since:
    0.18.8
